	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I am really thankfull, the bubble was broken (sure that I broke it desoldering the old rom chip) and didn't connect both traces (cartridge connector and sram pin) so pin D1 was floating, but now is working perfect.
<br />thanks

		

		</td>
	</tr>
